Muchidzidzo che[[Taranyika]], [[chitsuwa]] (island in English) ishoko rinoreva nzvimbo yakatendedzwa nemvura ingava pakati pe[[gungwa]]; [[nyanza]] kana rwizi. Chitsuwa chinosiyana ne"Continent" pakuti chidiki.

MuAfrica kune zvitsuwa zvinoti: Madagascar; Mauritius; Zanzibar; Equitorial Guinea; Cape Verde; Seychelles; Victoria Island nezvimwewo. Pasi rose chitsuwa chihombesa ndicho chinonzi [[Greenland]].
